IANAPwTypeTC.name: IANAPwTypeTC
IANAPwTypeTC.description: Indicates the PW type (i.e., the carried service).

IANAPwPsnTypeTC.name: IANAPwPsnTypeTC
IANAPwPsnTypeTC.description: Identifies the PSN type that the PW will use over the network.

IANAPwCapabilities.name: IANAPwCapabilities
IANAPwCapabilities.description: This TC describes a collection of capabilities related to a specific PW. Values may be added in the future based on new capabilities introduced in IETF documents.
